01:18:09.960 --> 01:18:13.250
crystal clear, and it is life

01:18:13.250 --> 01:18:13.260
flowing

01:18:13.260 --> 01:18:16.910
today; it's coming fast.

01:18:16.920 --> 01:18:18.890
It's life.

01:18:18.900 --> 01:18:21.950
That word, Pastor George, that you got for

01:18:21.960 --> 01:18:24.350
this meeting about persistence

01:18:24.360 --> 01:18:28.390
in

01:18:28.390 --> 01:18:28.400
prayer—just

01:18:28.400 --> 01:18:31.310
keep praying.

01:18:31.320 --> 01:18:34.070
Now, it would take a group of men to move

01:18:34.080 --> 01:18:36.649
