01:19:04.520 --> 01:19:07.669
Obstinate things.

01:19:09.120 --> 01:19:12.590
People are moved away

01:19:12.600 --> 01:19:14.390
from what they need to be moved away

01:19:14.400 --> 01:19:16.850
from and carried to what they need to be

01:19:16.860 --> 01:19:18.350
