01:19:18.360 --> 01:19:21.350
There goes another one

01:19:21.360 --> 01:19:23.689
floating down the river.

01:19:23.699 --> 01:19:26.630
We can move it with the Holy Ghost.

01:19:26.640 --> 01:19:29.630
He needs to move that car real quick.

01:19:29.640 --> 01:19:35.630
That one wants to get out of the flow.

01:19:41.100 --> 01:19:45.350
Look, there are some

01:19:45.350 --> 01:19:45.360
more—that

01:19:45.360 --> 01:19:48.470
persistence, perpetual persistence,

01:19:48.480 --> 01:19:51.350
