01:20:14.930 --> 01:20:14.940
and

01:20:14.940 --> 01:20:17.510
there

01:20:17.510 --> 01:20:17.520
are

01:20:17.520 --> 01:20:19.189
some

01:20:19.199 --> 01:20:21.410
stubborn situations,

01:20:21.420 --> 01:20:24.790
but the river can do the work.

01:20:24.800 --> 01:20:28.970
Hallelujah.

01:20:28.980 --> 01:20:32.570
Pastor George, I believe that

01:20:32.580 --> 01:20:36.050
