01:20:42.120 --> 01:20:45.110
we have tsunamis of rivers and we

01:20:45.120 --> 01:20:48.350
also, in addition, have that wave that's

01:20:48.360 --> 01:20:53.950
coming from the very heart of God.

01:20:53.960 --> 01:20:56.330
Can we just go ahead and start praying

01:20:56.340 --> 01:20:58.270
